br />\n著墨得最多嘅都係有關女性嘅身份認同同處世<br />\nComing of age嘅時候尋找自己<br />\n我覺得都係好作品<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8075eff1660bc342bc8fa87cdc00b0c1a2be63c9","tid":1812622,"uid":59818,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"9725d8f791853ed1f0593efc0672d89b845c6fc9","tid":1812622,"uid":28584,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-02-09T00:33:42.000Z","msg":"有劇透<br />\n<br />\n之前都睇左Lady Bird <br />\n感覺Greta Thunberg真係好鍾意Saoirse同Timothee呢對螢幕情侶 <br />\n然後兩套戲佢地都係冇一齊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n但又唔覺可惜喎 始終今次Jo好明顯唔係愛Laurie⋯對比起教授 連屋企人都即刻話佢係鍾意佢<br />\n我覺得啲人物塑造得算幾立體<br />\n唔會憎得落啲角色<br />\n就算有人會話Amy插足Laurie同Jo之間 <br />\n但其實都好多野顯示到佢暗戀Laurie好多年<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/ass.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n同埋結婚又唔係佢主動嘅 <br />\n唯一可以話嘅係佢甘心做Laurie水抱囉<br />\n<br />\n其實無論Lady Bird定Little Women <br />\n愛情都唔算係主線 <br />\n著墨得最多嘅都係有關女性嘅身份認同同處世<br />\nComing of age嘅時候尋找自己<br />\n我覺得都係好作品<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-02-09T00:48:47.000Z","msg":"hoe dare you<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a874141f654936236ac1daa9bfa09e528114e6e1","tid":1812622,"uid":28584,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"8075eff1660bc342bc8fa87cdc00b0c1a2be63c9","tid":1812622,"uid":59818,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"9725d8f791853ed1f0593efc0672d89b845c6fc9","tid":1812622,"uid":28584,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-02-09T00:33:42.000Z","msg":"有劇透<br />\n<br />\n之前都睇左Lady Bird <br />\n感覺Greta Thunberg真係好鍾意Saoirse同Timothee呢對螢幕情侶 <br />\n然後兩套戲佢地都係冇一齊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n但又唔覺可惜喎 始終今次Jo好明顯唔係愛Laurie⋯對比起教授 連屋企人都即刻話佢係鍾意佢<br />\n我覺得啲人物塑造得算幾立體<br />\n唔會憎得落啲角色<br />\n就算有人會話Amy插足Laurie同Jo之間 <br />\n但其實都好多野顯示到佢暗戀Laurie好多年<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/ass.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n同埋結婚又唔係佢主動嘅 <br />\n唯一可以話嘅係佢甘